nodes.text: Epsilon 5 was a call sign used by the First Order. During the attack on the Ottegan-populated world of Arthon, a male stormtrooper of the First Order piloted a TIE/fo space superiority fighter under the callsign Epsilon 5. During the battle, a missile from an Ottegan siege engine struck Epsilon 5, making it the eighth recorded First Order casualty of the battle.
